  "detailed_description": "<h1>GAMES BY THE CREATOR OF INVADER TD</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609780/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1681821204\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609780/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1681821204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609780/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1681821204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Invader TD brings the classic tower defense experience to a side scrolling environment, manage your resources to strategically build your defenses and defend against enemy attacks while evolving to be able to conquer planet earth.<br><br>You are in control of an alien race that aims to dominate planet Earth, but the human beings will not let that happen, use your skills to defend yourself from human attacks, building structures and evolving them.<br><br><strong>Build Towers</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609780/extras/50aa171241b85dc62053470c06ab0683.poster.avif?t=1681821204\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609780/extras/50aa171241b85dc62053470c06ab0683.webm?t=1681821204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609780/extras/50aa171241b85dc62053470c06ab0683.mp4?t=1681821204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Upgrade Towers</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609780/extras/413801027df215c05adef1179868a20e.poster.avif?t=1681821204\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609780/extras/413801027df215c05adef1179868a20e.webm?t=1681821204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609780/extras/413801027df215c05adef1179868a20e.mp4?t=1681821204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Destroy the enemies</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609780/extras/5463dcf024b38170c0470cb6940c85eb.poster.avif?t=1681821204\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609780/extras/5463dcf024b38170c0470cb6940c85eb.webm?t=1681821204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609780/extras/5463dcf024b38170c0470cb6940c85eb.mp4?t=1681821204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609780/extras/5b4fa4a02c2fbb6f1af599b11a184fe4.avif?t=1681821204\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Exciting battles<br></li><li> Physics based<br></li><li> Stylized pixel art<br></li><li> 4 towers types<br></li><li> 10+ enemies types<br></li><li> Original soundtrack</li></ul>",
